00:05.795 --> 00:08.478
Normally between 6:30 and 7 o'clock in the morning...

00:08.563 --> 00:10.903
...and then I first have a cup of coffee.

00:11.937 --> 00:14.075
How many pairs of Adidas do you own?

00:15.341 --> 00:18.535
I don't know exactly, to be honest, but I think it's close to a hundred.

00:19.691 --> 00:20.922
What's your favorite pair?

00:21.711 --> 00:22.445
Stan Smiths.

00:23.321 --> 00:24.689
I have tons of them.

00:25.870 --> 00:28.295
Americans pronounce the brand name Adidas.

00:28.693 --> 00:29.614
How do you feel about that?

00:30.607 --> 00:32.694
I don't mind as long as they buy our shoes.

00:33.355 --> 00:34.715
What did you wanna be when you grew up?

00:35.395 --> 00:36.664
A professional football player.

00:37.212 --> 00:41.790
My name is Herbert Hainer and I am happy to be the CEO of Adidas.

